about_the_job:
Job Requirements:
Minimum D3 (Diploma) in Computer Engineering/Informatics/Electrical Engineering;
Minimum 2 (two) years of experience in the field of developing main application systems, primarily ERP (not just website development);
Proficiency and experience in developing application systems using .Net programming languages (ASP, VB, C#);
Mastery of SQL Server database and the use of Stored Procedures;
Proficiency in Crystal Report;
Proficiency in other programming languages such as PHP or Javascript is a plus but not mandatory;
Proficiency in other databases such as MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQL lite is a plus but not mandatory;
Ability to analyze problems and provide solutions, high attention to detail, enthusiasm for learning new technologies, and the ability to work well both in a team and individually.
Placement in Medan, North Sumatra
